matchOpSig

protected MetaMBean.OperationSignature matchOpSig(MetaMBean.OperationSignature[] opSigs,
                                                  Object... args)
Attempts to match the passed argument array against one of the OperationSignatures in the passed OperationSignature array

Parameters:
opSigs - An array of OperationSignatures that have the same number of arguments
args - The array of arguments to find a matching OperationSignature for
Returns:
A matching OperationSignature or null if one was not found. If more than one match, a RuntimeException will be thrown.
